{"tid":1538963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候去返冷兵器時代","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:02:39.000Z","uid":137217,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8512688cf0431ac24a48ad8403633ebfa0068ea7","tid":1538963,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:25:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lny2kS-IuYU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLny2kS-IuYU&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=f4d5a382\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Lny2kS-IuYU</a><br />\n<br />\n認真e舊野有得諗<br />\n只要加大個絞盤同繩既力已經可以加強威力<br />\n制作容易,有木工就得<br />\n材料都好簡單,木頭同麻繩<br />\n棄咗都唔肉痛<br />\n係個底加幾個碌行得走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人手磚咁廢<br />\ne舊野...有得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903afed360aeace8cbbab7210136a1926aad5491","tid":1538963,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:26:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e90e4e3e3879e0546d710ab2facf2aa199435996","tid":1538963,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:26:48.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4176bd38190a200a637f78ecca4a98119ea8d6","tid":1538963,"u